data.description: Immediate possession on this adorable 4BD, 2.5BA ranch in Heath Schools! This home has so much to offer. There is a huge fenced in backyard with an over sized 15X20 out building that has electric and french doors. With a little creativity the possibilities are endless with what it could become! 4 spacious bedrooms with 3 of them having original hardwood floors. Upgrades include new flooring, A/C and stainless steel appliances. The full basement has a wood burning stove, full bathroom, laundry, storage area and rec room. 1 car attached garage.  Washer, dryer, and all kitchen appliances convey. The kitchen has tons of cabinet space and a large pantry! Within walking distance to Geller Park and Stevenson Elementary school.
